      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and will require a major overhaul, and the transmission is starting to slip. It is currently driveable for short distances only and will need a trailer for any long-distance transport.",
