    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies both mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure peak performance and long-term reliability for its next owner. Featuring a sophisticated interior and a robust powertrain, it offers an exceptional driving experience without compromise. We invite discerning buyers to appreciate the superior handling and proven durability of this quintessential model.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a charm\u2014perfect for your daily commute or weekend adventures. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it's ready to hit the road with its next owner right away. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! I'm super happy to answer any questions you have. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example has been meticulously maintained for performance, with the critical rod bearing service and subframe reinforcement already completed. The drivetrain features a precise 6-speed manual transmission feeding a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension has been upgraded with a Bilstein PSS10 coilover kit for improved dampening and roll center adjustment. It rides on staggered alloy wheels with recent Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. While the exterior shows minor road-derived character, the engine vitals and chassis rigidity remain top-tier for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor road-wear one would expect from a carefully driven car. Inside, the leather upholstery remains supple and clean, with all electronic features and climate controls functioning exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has been serviced regularly, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that still delivers plenty of power. You\u2019ll find the suspension firm yet comfortable, providing a confident ride. It has been garage-kept and smoke-free, making it an ideal choice for someone seeking a reliable, high-quality vehicle without the new-car price tag. Recent fluid changes and a thorough multi-point inspection ensure it is ready for its next owner to drive away today.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to offer this impeccably maintained vehicle, presenting a distinguished profile and robust mechanical integrity. Rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards, this specimen delivers a refined driving experience characterized by consistent performance and aesthetic preservation. A premier selection for the professional seeking a reliable, high-caliber automotive investment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable daily driver, and it\u2019s ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-cared for over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this car is a joy to drive and still looks fantastic. I\u2019ve absolutely loved owning it, and I know you will too. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2005 BMW M3, a definitive example of the E46 chassis. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six engine, utilizing individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing to produce a linear, high-revving power band. This unit is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock for precise torque distribution. Essential preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system refresh with an aluminum radiator. The suspension geometry remains true, providing exceptional lateral grip and feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed in for peak performance. This is a driver-focused machine with a focus on mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
